rvice/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"「在民主體制內，強制要求非軍事人員為你打仗，我不知道這樣做有甚麼意思。那是活生生的人命，平民百姓不應牽涉在內，承受戰爭的後果。」<br />\n<br />\n都幾撚on9<br />\n覆巢之下 復有完卵乎<br />\n和平得太耐 大家啲國民身分認同好差"},{"pid":"a8bd9ee50749bca6000616742e318c148ea3d630","tid":1814282,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"美國應該要大規模使用AI機械人士兵"},{"pid":"504fbca3a9946f382a67e18ad64bbebadbc180e0","tid":1814282,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:49:15.000Z","msg":"難以相信美國進入2020年代仲需要真人落場打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現代戰美國靠空襲都搞掂大量目標<br />\n<br />\n想精準打擊咪出小型無人機遙控接近地面打囉<br />\n<br />\n連online 夾公仔都做得到極少控制delay<br />\n<br />\n唔信美國外星科技做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2164901091314c441b3def21a50dfc0843abf24","tid":1814282,"uid":308414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a26cf79fad09a8939feeb605382e340e448c99a3","tid":1814282,"uid":33848,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:43:17.000Z","msg":"就算打支那全面戰都唔撚洗徵兵啦<br />\n咁高軍費你估假架<br />\n佢地究竟知唔知現役人數有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032bbecdabd0c1d6cf6fc768e5ac8358dab32782","tid":1814282,"uid":322732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"如果美國係香港徵兵北上打仗應該大把人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f29dcb5cb635147441f45925771ca621d43acf","tid":1814282,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"揾我地參軍啦屌"},{"pid":"2aabe9636035e14ae08432e8e5b58e0065958ae6","tid":1814282,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"美軍整咁多科技就係知人命重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal